text.tspan: Prevalence of schizophrenia by age, World
Share of population within each age group suffering from schizophrenia. This is measured across both sexes. Figures
attempt to provide a true estimate (going beyond reported diagnosis) of schizophrenia prevalence based on medical,
epidemiological data, surveys and meta-regression modelling.
Source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease
